
'''Souleymane Sylla,''' ni umukinnyi wa firime ukomoka muri Gineya ariko utuye mubutaliyani . <ref>https://en.unifrance.org/directories/person/394944/souleymane-sylla</ref> Azwi cyane ku ruhare rwe muri filime ''Les princes de la ville'', ''Shiny Happy People'' na ''Tolo Tolo'' . <ref>https://mubi.com/cast/souleymane-sylla</ref> <ref>http://www.agence-adequat.com/fiche.cfm/115-2_679547_souleymane_sylla.html</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavukiye muri [[Gineya]] nyuma yimukira mu Butaliyani. 

== Umwuga ==
Souleymane Sylla yakuriyee muri gineya  aho yamaze akiri muto. Yari afite imyaka 8 igihe umuryango wimukiye i Créteil. Ku ishuri ryisumbuye rya Simone de Beauvoir niho yavumbuye ikinamico. Nyuma yaho, yinjiye mu kigo cy’imyidagaduro cy’Abafaransa cyatoranijwe kandi kizwi cyane. Yagize uruhare mu gufungura ubudasa muri theatre, cyane cyane muri TNS i Strasbourg. Yerekanwe n'umuyobozi Blandine Savetier, yahawe akazi mu mushinga wa serial ya Odyssey, yerekanwe mu bice 13, hanze, mu iserukiramuco rya Avignon 2019. Kuva mu 2013, tumubona muri firime nyinshi ngufi, harimo Anthropologiya yumuntu ugezweho, Amabwiriza yumugani no Gukata umwenda, aho akinamo uruhare runini. Yimukiye mu buyobozi muri 2012 hamwe na Mchinda, l'invaincu, akurikirwa na 2015 na Le Costume na Les Princes de la ville muri 2016. Nk’uruhare runini, yakinnye mu Budage muri firime ya TV yitwa Penthesilea na Maximilian Villwock Mu mwaka wa 2019, yagaragaye muri filime ya Jérémie Elkaïm, Ils sont vivants, itarasohoka mu Bufaransa kugeza nyuma yimyaka ibiri kubera icyorezo cya Covid-19. Mu 2020, yakinnye muri filime yo gusetsa yo mu Butaliyani Tolo Tolo akina 'Oumar'. Iyi filime yabaye iyamamare ryinjije umunsi wa mbere miliyoni 8.7.<ref>https://www.gapfilm.ir/people/7034-souleymane-sylla</ref>

